rows.label: qev056103_MSG0001
rows.name: You are...human? Ah. Sent by On'tonam.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056103_MSG0002
rows.name:
I am sorry... You have come all this way, but...
my Ovah has already begun...to fade.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056103_MSG0003
rows.name: Heh...heh. For the first time, I am...free of its bonds...[ST:wait ]
